{"tid":1540204,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【緊急！】轉風向！轉風向！","createTime":"2019-09-04T11:00:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T11:20:26.000Z","uid":312473,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a5989846a63af24dee59f673378a805e440f615a","tid":1540204,"uid":312473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:00:35.000Z","msg":"睇完林奠話撤回條例之後，而我地既立場同訴求亦好清晰！<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n大家都知道林奠打呢張牌係為左<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">轉風向</span></span></strong>！！想為9/9號爭取機會！<br />\n-------------<br />\n隔離亦有post開左分析林奠背後用意係咩！大家入去睇下<br />\n[六大陰謀］林鄭宣布撤回反送中的陰謀<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1539227\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1539227</a><br />\n<br />\n宣布撤回條例並不是因為我們，而是為了讓「美國」能夠看見的「善意」。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1539399\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1539399</a><br />\n---------------<br />\n<br />\n依家我地<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">緊急</span></span></strong>要做既就係<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">大量係Twitter Reddit 到輸出文宣！<br />\n<br />\n1. 向國際揭穿林奠政府既真面目<br />\n<br />\n2. 大大聲話俾國際聽我地要啲咩</div></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔好俾林奠帶到風向！！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣組全面進場！距離9/9時間唔多！一點要將<span style=\"color: blue;\">國際風向</span>帶返來我地到</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我地要大大力兜巴車落林奠政府到！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"760e613ad355492f2a0f850127cff833791cfaac","tid":1540204,"uid":312833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:01:17.000Z","msg":"不收貨，繼續爭取。但暫時轉和理非。"},{"pid":"92a4480315d52b9699edf83d14a9076fed6765bd","tid":1540204,"uid":141980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:01:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a1a8a301426b9e6a814451ace4777e348e7c1bc0","tid":1540204,"uid":258210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:02:34.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\nbin個袋住先我就同bin個割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f3093175aa1d286a9cb04afad00bef4cb78c9e0","tid":1540204,"uid":272580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:03:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">絕不重蹈司徒華年代港人再犯的錯。</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>絕不與魔鬼做交易。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求！缺一不可</span>"},{"pid":"a2b4e228c48778a4f0a078946cd41f1048d52895","tid":1540204,"uid":175788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:05:06.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n缺一不可</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"eb6a1e8c9d16f05686c7fb0f081ef7c227841196","tid":1540204,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:05:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭宣布撤回送中條例的六大陰謀</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1539227\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1539227</a><br />\n快啲同我入黎睇曬佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=